1. Product Vision
Build a Slack-native execution intelligence platform that:
• Automatically ingests execution context from multiple work tools
 • Extracts structured insights
 • Applies configurable redaction & sensitivity policies
 • Generates high-quality narrative drafts
 • Enables human-in-loop publishing
 • Compounds a structured execution knowledge graph
This is NOT a LinkedIn tool.
It is:
Execution → Structured Insight → Controlled Expression.

2. Target Users
Primary:
 • Growth teams
 • GTM ops
 • Head of Growth
 • Early-stage operators
Secondary:
 • Founders
Workspace-based SaaS.

3. Core Product Philosophy
Slack = Primary Interaction Surface
 Dashboard = Configuration + Control + History
 Multi-Source = Background Intelligence Layer

