12. Security Architecture
Mandatory:
• AES-256 at rest
 • TLS in transit
 • OAuth token encryption
 • RLS for org isolation
 • Signed Slack requests
 • Audit logs
 • Configurable retention (7/30/90 days)
 • Raw transcript deletion after processing (optional)
No auto-posting without approval.

